      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>mirin</strong>, <strong>half </strong>of<strong> </strong>the <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong>, the juice of the<strong> lime<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong>and mix it all together – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p>",
