    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> king prawns</strong> and <strong>edamame beans</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until cooked through</p><p>Once cooked, add the <strong>remaining toasted sesame oil</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p>",
